verses.text: \w The|strong="H1732"\w* heavens declare \w the|strong="H1732"\w* glory \w of|strong="H4210"\w* God; \w And|strong="H1732"\w* \w the|strong="H1732"\w* firmament showeth \w his|strong="H1732"\w* handiwork.
Day \w unto|strong="H5046"\w* day uttereth speech, \w And|strong="H8064"\w* night \w unto|strong="H5046"\w* night showeth knowledge.
\w There|strong="H3117"\w* \w is|strong="H3117"\w* no speech \w nor|strong="H3117"\w* language; \w Their|strong="H3117"\w* voice \w is|strong="H3117"\w* not heard.

\w Their|strong="H8085"\w* line \w is|strong="H1697"\w* gone out \w through|strong="H6963"\w* \w all|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* earth, \w And|strong="H6963"\w* \w their|strong="H8085"\w* \w words|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* end \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* world. \w In|strong="H8085"\w* \w them|strong="H8085"\w* \w hath|strong="H1697"\w* \w he|strong="H1697"\w* set \w a|strong="H3068"\w* tabernacle \w for|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* sun,

\w Which|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* \w as|strong="H3318"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bridegroom \w coming|strong="H3318"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w* \w of|strong="H3605"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* chamber, \w And|strong="H3318"\w* rejoiceth \w as|strong="H3318"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* strong \w man|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w run|strong="H7097"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* course.

\w His|strong="H3318"\w* \w going|strong="H3318"\w* \w forth|strong="H3318"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w from|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* \w end|strong="H3318"\w* \w of|strong="H1368"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* heavens, \w And|strong="H3318"\w* \w his|strong="H3318"\w* circuit \w unto|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* ends \w of|strong="H1368"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w*; \w And|strong="H3318"\w* there \w is|strong="H1931"\w* nothing hidden \w from|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* heat thereof.

\w The|strong="H5921"\w* law \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H4161"\w* perfect, restoring \w the|strong="H5921"\w* soul: \w The|strong="H5921"\w* testimony \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H4161"\w* sure, making wise \w the|strong="H5921"\w* simple.

\w The|strong="H3068"\w* precepts \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w right|strong="H3068"\w*, rejoicing \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w heart|strong="H5315"\w*: \w The|strong="H3068"\w* commandment \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* pure, enlightening \w the|strong="H3068"\w* eyes.

\w The|strong="H3068"\w* fear \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w clean|strong="H1249"\w*, enduring forever: \w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w ordinances|strong="H4687"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H5869"\w* \w true|strong="H3068"\w*, \add and\add* \w righteous|strong="H3477"\w* altogether.

More \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* desired \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w than|strong="H3068"\w* gold, yea, \w than|strong="H3068"\w* much fine gold; Sweeter \w also|strong="H3068"\w* \w than|strong="H3068"\w* honey \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* droppings \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* honeycomb.

Moreover \w by|strong="H2091"\w* them \w is|strong="H2091"\w* \w thy|strong="H2530"\w* servant warned: \w In|strong="H7227"\w* keeping them there \w is|strong="H2091"\w* \w great|strong="H7227"\w* reward.
\w Who|strong="H5650"\w* \w can|strong="H5650"\w* discern \add his\add* errors? Clear thou \w me|strong="H8104"\w* \w from|strong="H5650"\w* hidden \add faults\add*.

Keep back \w thy|strong="H5641"\w* servant also \w from|strong="H5352"\w* presumptuous \add sins\add*; Let them not have dominion over \w me|strong="H5641"\w*: Then \w shall|strong="H4310"\w* I be upright, \w And|strong="H5352"\w* I \w shall|strong="H4310"\w* be \w clear|strong="H5352"\w* \w from|strong="H5352"\w* great transgression.

Let \w the|strong="H1571"\w* words \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w my|strong="H5650"\w* mouth \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w the|strong="H1571"\w* meditation \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w my|strong="H5650"\w* heart \w Be|strong="H1571"\w* acceptable \w in|strong="H7227"\w* \w thy|strong="H2820"\w* sight, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w*, \w my|strong="H5650"\w* rock, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w my|strong="H5650"\w* redeemer.
